{"TopicId":213278,"ForumId":119,"TopicTitle":"Anyone else bothered by the Immediacy of Pretentious Kerman\u0026#039;s Unnecessary Crash Report blocking your view of the Glorious Destruction?","CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T18:02:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T18:02:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/EAA3W8kKhuw?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Let us see the destruction!\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/LtniY4VzkZ4?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Uppity Kerman\u0027s Unnecessary Report\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/lm0MVTIosPA?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Flight Report Pops up too early.\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a lot of work done by the artists to make the rockets and explosions look good.\u00A0 But this pop-up (and especially it\u0027s immediacy) takes the Kerbal fun out of Epically Failing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/203961-developer-insights-10-%E2%80%93-collisions/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EDeveloper Insights 10\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/200605-developer-insights-2-%E2%80%93-visual-effects/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EDeveloper Insights 2\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe huge, screen hogging Flight Report is too big, too immediate and too opaque in my opinion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone else bothered by this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-11T02:12:54Z\u0022 title=\u002203/11/2023 02:12  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 11, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by JoeSchmuckatelli\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T18:40:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I noticed that too.\u00A0 Several times it stopped the game and told me the craft had been destroyed, even when it was clearly intact and I had to reload.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T20:06:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is weird is that I\u0027ve had a couple of plane RUDs where only a wheel survived and no crash report popped up.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe it\u0027s only affecting rockets?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T23:03:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224246494\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022213278\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677528396\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is weird is that I\u0027ve had a couple of plane RUDs where only a wheel survived and no crash report popped up.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe it\u0027s only affecting rockets?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat happens to me all the time. The steerable non-retractable plane wheel is immortal and will survive anything and the camera will always go to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI agree though, that pop up window is counter productive. At least let the player watch what is happening.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nI am drawing a blank but the same kind of window that pops up in KSP1 works better for reasons I can\u2019t think of.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T23:10:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224246757\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022213278\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677539027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe steerable non-retractable plane wheel is immortal\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s the part!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas a mind of it\u0027s own!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DadJokeCinema","CreatedById":226590,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-28T14:43:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t have anything to add to this topic, I believe it should be delayed for a few seconds after crash (it\u0027s the fastest loading part of the game for me right now), but I wanted to praise this topic title as it\u0027s made me laugh like five times now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"B15hop","CreatedById":68462,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-28T19:35:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t tell me I crashed. I know I crashed.. Trust me, I know..lol. I will hit Escape or quick load or whatever, whenever I am done watching the explodey goodness, which is what KSP is built on. My two cents. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-04T14:05:00Z\u0022 title=\u002203/04/2023 02:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 4, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by B15hop\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}